author: Ben Collins
title: Australian Ebola veteran chooses COVID-19 in Cambodia over economic uncertainty at home
description: While other Australians clamoured to flee Cambodia, this man chose to use his experience working for the Red Cross in Africa to protect his family from coronavirus and economic hardship.
